    {
      "id": "rule-dl9a2c4f-8b3e-4d1a-a5f6-1c7e3db82f01",
      "type": "rule",
      "text": "SIN-InkogniFlow Dual-Logger is the canonical human-to-agent recording system: all workflow recording must use sin-flow record-dual (OS logger via pynput + browser logger via JS injection → Flask merge server on :5000 → agent_workflow_master.json). Replay must use sin-flow replay with Bézier mouse curves, Gaussian jitter, and CDP/pyautogui/hybrid modes. Never build alternative recording pipelines.",
